Need Help. Whats the best way to get rid of the rust and re-season these cast iron pans..
Put them in a self cleaning oven for an hour or two. Then get a drill and attach a wire brush cup and sand it.
OOoooo very good idea. The rust wont affect anything inside my oven will it?? lol
